## Installation

‚ö†Ô∏è **WARNING:** Ephemerista is pre-release software and has not been fully validated, yet. _Use at your own risk_.

Install Ephemerista via `pip` in a new virtual environment in the current directory:

```shell
python -m venv .venv
source .venv/bin/activate
pip install ephemerista
```

